WEBVTT

00:15:25.981 --> 00:15:33.783
da kažemo da imamo sjajnu zemlju
sa neverovatnim idealima,

00:15:33.783 --> 00:15:36.762
radili smo naporno
i napravili neki napredak,

00:15:36.762 --> 00:15:39.932
ali nismo gotovi.

00:15:39.932 --> 00:15:43.926
Još uvek imamo u sebi one stare ideje

00:15:43.926 --> 00:15:46.967
o superiornosti, što prouzrokuje

00:15:46.967 --> 00:15:50.439
da to ugrađujemo u naše institucije,

00:15:50.439 --> 00:15:52.418
u naše društvo i generacije,

00:15:52.418 --> 00:15:56.027
i to prouzrokuje očajanje

00:15:56.027 --> 00:16:03.151
i nejednakosti i obezvređivanje
mladih crnaca.